data.description: Come home to this beautiful newly built home (2023).  Beautiful woodwork throughout along with all the newest finishes.  Backyard woods.  4 stall wide garage.  3 upstairs bedrooms including a Master Suite with walk in closet and Master Bath.  2 more floors to finish when desired, including the possibility of 5 bedrooms.  Gorgeous stone fireplace.  Great neighborhood and close to Hwy 10 and trips to metro area. Come see this house asap before it is gone!
